@startuml C4_Pattern_EventCorrelation
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml

title YAWL Workflow Pattern - Event-Based Execution

Boundary(workflow, "Workflow") {
    Component(event_task, "EventTask", "Task", "Wait for event")
    Component(correlation_set, "CorrelationSet", "Data", "Matching criteria")
}

Boundary(event_mgmt, "Event Management") {
    Component(event_listener, "EventListener", "Subscribe", "Listen for events")
    Component(event_correlator, "EventCorrelator", "Match", "Match correlation data")
    Component(event_queue, "EventQueue", "Buffer", "Queued events")
    Component(timeout_handler, "TimeoutHandler", "Safety", "Max wait time")
}

Boundary(events, "Event Sources") {
    Component(external_system, "External System", "Source", "Sends events")
    Component(message_broker, "MessageBroker", "Broker", "Event distribution")
}

Boundary(continuation, "Continuation") {
    Component(event_retrieved, "EventRetrieved", "Outcome", "Event matched")
    Component(timeout_exceeded, "TimeoutExceeded", "Outcome", "Timeout occurred")
    Component(next_task, "NextTask", "Task", "Continue workflow")
}

event_task --> correlation_set: Uses for matching
correlation_set --> event_listener: Defines criteria
event_listener --> event_correlator: Correlates events
external_system --> message_broker: Sends events
message_broker --> event_queue: Buffers events
event_queue --> event_correlator: Matches against

event_correlator --> event_retrieved: If matched
timeout_handler --> timeout_exceeded: If timeout
event_retrieved --> next_task: Continues
timeout_exceeded --> next_task: With default

Note as N1
Event Correlation Pattern:
1. Task waits for specific event
2. Define correlation criteria (order ID, user ID)
3. External system sends events
4. Correlator matches event to task
5. Multiple events queued simultaneously
6. Timeout safety: max 30 minutes
7. Continue with matched event data

Use Cases:
- Order fulfillment waiting for shipment confirmation
- Loan approval waiting for document upload
- Claim processing waiting for verification
End note

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml
